Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:05.65,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,The wedding rings embedded around Jojo's heart and throat
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:08.31,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,cannot be removed through surgical means.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:11.92,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,They will dissolve and release poison into Jojo's body in 33 days, {from yubiwa until sareru mae ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:15.86,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,unless he can obtain the antidotes by defeating both ACDC and Wham.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What the Hell have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was blowing smoke up their arses \Nwhen I said I'd be ready in a month! {from hattari until nano ni yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And they bought my bluff! {aitsura honki ni toriyagatte}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've said "one year" instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Jojo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.22,0:00:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you even joke about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me help {\i1}you{\i0} and think of something already! {shinken ni kangaettendarou na}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I {\i1}am{\i0} thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no use crying over spilt milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We both need to keep calm in order to carry on, Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, you'll need to be able to perform the exact same act I'm about to show you. {from jojo until ikenai}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The water's not pouring out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a try. {jojo hore}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the water from pouring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's face some facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of our Ripple powers, we're almost equal in strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but {\i1}you{\i0} always purge all of your powers out of your palms!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That lack of control caused the water to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I channeled my powers into my fingertips, those single points of contact. {from shikashi until houshutsu shitano da}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Those {\i1}single{\i0} concentrated points! {itten shuuchuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus your energy into these single points, and you'll cause the water to oscillate within the glass, {from itten until ga deki}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,effectively trapping the liquid within. {from mizu until ochinai}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But increase your contact area, and your excess Ripple energy causes the water to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The smaller the nozzle of a liquid gun, the further the liquid flies. {from mizuteppo until to iu koto da}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand, {\i1}Idiota{\i0}?! {wakatta ka sukatan}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for you to better control your Ripple powers, you need to undergo the formal Ripple Regimen. {from iika until naranai}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought you to Venice for this very reason, {sono tame ni koko e kita no da}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because my Ripple Master resides here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I hate breaking my back over work, that above all else, warrants effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey Caesar, ain't Venice more of a touristy-type of town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What would a Ripple Master be doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gondolier. {soko no kimi}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us to {\i1}isola di aria serbatoio{\i0}. {air supply isle = air supply the band}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gondolier, did you not hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's standing {\i1}on{\i0} his bloody oar over water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the Hell is this guy?! {na-nanda koitsu nanimono}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Crikey! {nanda}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Arsehole! {kono yarou}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the Hell did I do to deserve a decking?! {from wake until ni wa}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're cruising for a bruising!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My{\i0}, at least you're capable of using Ripple energy to stand on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman is known as Lisa Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her real name, personal history, family, {from honmyou until katei}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the motivation behind her mastery of the Art of Mystics remain a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, Lisa Lisa will devote the \Nnext month to training Jojo and myself! {from daga until ni naru no da}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You still ain't off the hook for hitting me head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna pull any punches, even if you are a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen your spectacular talents for myself {\i1}with{\i0} this oar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You even have my compliments for managing your waddle over water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if you expect to become a respectable Ripple user within a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to dispose yourself to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The water's hardened into a pair of pillars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Joseph Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For the next month, you'll have to wear that Ripple \NRespirator for your Ripple Regimen all day, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't br-! {i-iki ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Find your respiratory rhythm. {kokyuu no rizumu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you have your rhythm, you'll have no issue respiring through the Ripple Respirator. {from rizumu until dekimasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you lose it, the respirator's valves will close, and you will suffer from suffocation. {from shikashi until ni natteimasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be capable of running 100 \Nkilometers while wearing that respirator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bollocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this bloody thing off-!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't breathe! {i-iki ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ripple Regimen has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The only relief you'll receive is during meals and when brushing your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jojo, find your rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have any problems breathing once you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why I oughta bust you up good, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:47.09,Over,,0,0,0,,There's another important thing that need be noted. {from sore until ga arimasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not teaching you the Art of \NMystics to save you from death, {until oshieru no de wa nai}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm teaching you because I need people capable of killing the Pillar Men! {until to iu koto}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You goddamn, selfish... {k-kono kono}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You want Maestra to mess you up some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hit women!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Formally, I would like to welcome you both
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to Venice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's earned the title of Ripple Master, but I would never wed a mistress like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a cute quality about her... {chotto mabui hito ga na}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny you should say that, Casanova. {nanda onna tarashi no temee ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} so respectful towards that broad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect the Maestra as much as I do my own mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't demean her, or {\i1}I{\i0} will deck you. {burei wo suru na yo ore ga yurusan}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isola di aria serbatoio{\i0} {air supply tou}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is a small island located 30 minutes north of Venice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the vibrant views of Venice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,this island remains shrouded thick in mystique. {kuraki shinpisei juubun}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that very mystique is equally befitting of its very mysterious owner, Lisa Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This island will serve as our training ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That entire island is my very own villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me to be disposed to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but how bad could it actually be? {kore kara donna shuugyou ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Both you and Joseph are safe and sound. {from anato until jojo mo buji}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ask for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Great-Uncle, don't you dare tell Nanna Erina about those rings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You blab, and I'll turn you black n' blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where would I even begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The preliminary trial to the Ripple Regimen {shiren no prologue wa}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,begins with the "Pillar of Hell!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maestra, you would damn us to so daunting a trial already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I haven't attempted it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the trial that has claimed the lives of many trainees!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You either complete this trial, or you take a boat back to the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two fill me in on what's {\i1}what{\i0}, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What the bloody Hell is this "Pillar of Hell?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand after you've taken a tumble down this tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maestra, you wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole damn pillar's drenched in oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The objective of this trial is to climb up 24 \Nmeters to the top of this tower, barehanded. {from sude de until nobottekinasai}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way out is {\i1}up{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You must complete this trial, or you will die trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta reach the top of this slippery pillar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you outta your mind?! {kore wo noboru no ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.17,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,A trial designed to temper and test the tenacity of Ripple users!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.62,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,This trial is so infamously, yet so aptly named...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.62,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,the "Pillar of Hell!" {hell climb pillar}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is {\i0}trying{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm using all of my Ripple energy just to stick to this pillar. {until seippai de}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even moving my fingers a centimeter upwards is exhausting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I fall... {moshi ichido demo}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I fall from this pillar even once...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think I'd have enough stamina to try the climb again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're dead if we stay still! {matsu no wa uejini nomi}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're have to climb up! {ore mo jojo mo}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer you keep jumping, the sooner you'll be drained of your stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb up the pillar-!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit! {i-ikan}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't spare a breath, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Ripple Respiration went awry from just speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole trial is bollocks! {fuzakenja nee}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew fully that I lacked the power and \Ncontrol needed to climb this prick of a pillar! {from koko e kita until shitteru darou kuso}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That goddamn broad {ano onna}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,threw our arses down here without a second thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She just lost what respect I had left for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never wanted to pay back a woman before,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got plenty of ideas to toss \Naround me head before I reach the top! {from ue until kangaeteyaru}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plenty{\i0}! {chikusho}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a bunch of trainees died before they could make it to the top, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet they all died from stupidity! {noumiso tarinakatta noto chigau no}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} honor the sanctity of the trial, and abide by the following rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You may rely only on your Ripple energy and your bare hands to reach the top! {from kono hell until hanekaesu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All other methods are prohibited!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break, Lisa Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean to leave me here to die, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is{\i0} my first day of training after all! {until ichinichi me}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just trying to see if I actually make an honest attempt, right? {until tasukete kureru darou}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll lower a ladder later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was no pity in her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really will leave me in this pit to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit! {chikusho}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're a Ripple Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That beauty of yours ain't gonna save you from my impending wrath! {from yurusenee until komiageru ze}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.52,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,28 hours have elapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:31.75,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,Caesar is at the 15 meter mark, \Nwhereas Jojo remains at the very bottom. {from caesar until zero meter jiten}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:34.94,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,The rings will dissolve in 28 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a little more than a day already,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but Caesar's only made it about halfway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I really should be concerned about me own arse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even he's desperate to save his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar's fingers are the only things keeping him stuck to the pillar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,b-but it looks like they just might slip!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,His Ripple energy's nearly spent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Climb Caesar, climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no, he's slipping again! {m-mata hagaresou da}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's barely hanging on by his fingertips!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a moment, I think I just had an epiphany! {from m-masaka until ah ja nakatta no ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar's not in any danger of slipping at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not using his fingertips to prevent slippage! {until gyaku ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The smaller the nozzle of a liquid gun, the further the liquid flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think I get it now! {m-masaka tameshite miru ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've solved the riddle to controlling the Ripple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick! {kore ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I've used the Ripple to stick to the pillar! {from yatta until hamon de kutsuita zo}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that using both hands would add more friction and support my body better! {from tenohira until image ga atta}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bizarre, but I was actually thinking {\i1}backwards{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I concentrate my Ripple energy into each of my \Nfingers, adhesion to the points of contact increases! {from itten until tsuyoi}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I not realize this sooner?! {until nazo datta ze}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I know, I'm gonna climb this pillar here, {from wakatta until nobotteite}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and pay back that busty bitch in full!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jojo's finally found his rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.61,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,Since then, 24 more hours have elapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:23.71,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,Caesar is situated at the 18 meter mark, with Jojo behind him at the 16 meter mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:27.72,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,The rings will dissolve in 27 days!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know why Caesar's been taking his sweet time to climb beyond the 18 meter mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Past the middle mark, this whacky pillar warps upward! {from kono until shiteirunda}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every movement needs to be carefully calculated beyond here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The warped curvature of this pillar reminds me of its twisted owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:46.99,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,Three more hours have elapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.66,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,Caesar has reached the 19 meter mark, with Jojo only a meter behind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's a fissure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With just a smidge of space for my fingers to fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy oh boy, I can have a breather!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopie! {urepii}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Finally! I'm chuffed to bits for a breath! {yattaze h-hitoiki tsukeruze}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I press something?! {nani ka no switch no you da}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be... {masaka}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You may rely only on your Ripple energy and your bare hands to reach the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay sharp! Something's gonna shoot out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That smidge of space {\i1}was{\i0} a booby trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're barely sticking to this pillar as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,b-but how are we supposed to get past this now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:45.00,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,At the 20 meter mark of the 24-meter-tall pillar, an umbrella of oil spews forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The razor-sharp nature of this ultrahigh-pressure oil barrier makes it impossible to pass! {from kore wa until barrier}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's the matter, Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you angry with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry about the cock up, Caesar. {s-sumanai caesar}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}who{\i0} could've resisted reaching out for a chance to rest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet the architect was one \Ntwisted twat for putting that trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Played me like a fool! {hikkakeyagatte}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jojo was compelled to reach for that \Nfissure due to a lack of confidence... {until fuan dakara da}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But am I confident enough in my own powers, that I can overcome this trap?! {from dekiru until toppa suru koto ga}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only one way to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's standing perpendicular to the pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe my Ripples of Adhesion and Repulsion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm channeling adhesive Ripple energy into my feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,while channeling repulsive Ripple energy \Nthroughout my body for protection from the barrier! {from gyaku until shuuchuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can coordinate, control, and simultaneously channel opposing Ripple energies! {from kono seihantai until control suru}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But controlling opposing Ripple energies will be an impossible feat for Jojo to replicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He won't break through the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Hot damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad Caesar made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm not even sure if I could rival his refined technique! {from ga komatta ze until dekiru no ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.02,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,After nine more grueling hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:44.08,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,Caesar has finally reached the top of the pillar in 61 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jojo won't be able to hold on any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please halt the oil barrier's flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's impulsive by nature, and when he's at his wit's end, {from jojo until kake ni dete}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be driven by impulse to penetrate the oil barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And if he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sticking to this one spot ain't gonna stop that oil from spewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If he attempts to penetrate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be bisected from being blasted by ultrahigh-pressurized oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if he manages to repel the barrier's wave, {until rakka shite}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll fall to the bottom and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! {kusso}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all or nothing now! {ichi ka bachi ka no kake daze}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Jojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the rhythm of the beat, and the Ripple in my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jojo!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... {jojo masaka}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's using Ripple energy to repel the barrier's trough to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,ride the wave! {subetta}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The further the wave pushes me out, the weaker its pressure becomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to jump! {soko de}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the remaining momentum of the barrier's wave to reach that wall! {until jump}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't fall, and he even gained three meters from that jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,None have ever attempted to \Novercome the trial by riding the wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's rather clever for using the trap to \Ncompensate for his lack of control and technique. {from jibun until yatsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I made it! {y-yatta ze}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But goddamn! {dakedo kuso}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since this wall is located above the warped pillar's 20 meter mark, I doubt anyone ever made it here!{from dare mo until tame}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My exhaustion's wearing on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had less than an arms-length left, too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}M-My rhythm's gone... {ko-kokyuu ga mou}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and my respiration's a mess...! {midarechimatta ze}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't angry at you for triggering that trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maestra, please forgive me for lending him a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend away, Caesar... {sore wa ii kedo caesar}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but aren't you as equally exhausted as he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar, I'm begging you from the \Nbottom of my heart! Don't let me go! {tte onegai da te wo hanasanaide kure caesar}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:30.94,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,After ten seconds and 13 consecutive pleas for \NCaesar's assistance, Jojo reached the top of the pillar. {from juu byou go until seikou}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your horses, {\i1}Mistress{\i0} Lisa Lisa. {machi na lisa lisa no neechan yo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was stuck to that damn pillar, I thought up a few {\i1}decent{\i0} ways to pay you back. {from mijimetarashiku until kangaeteita ze}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've narrowed it down to {\i1}two{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I strip your clothes off, or should I pinch your nose until you cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought he was simpleton,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I suppose even he can bear a significant grudge. {igai to shunen bukai na koitsu wa}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick your poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can control and keep the water from spilling out of this glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magnifico{\i0}! {subarashii}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After these three trying days, he's finally got the gist of controlling the Ripple!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His talent is impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but even more impressive is the \NMaestra's ability draw out that talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm chuffed to bits! {k-kandou shita ze}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'd like to start the next trial, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll overcome anything you throw at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hard to figure. {wakaran}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you {\i1}are{\i0} just a simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fret not, for I have {\i1}plenty{\i0} of things to throw at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee that you'll be chuffed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, because the learning curve increases over the next three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blokes sneaking up behind me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:21:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The water's been gelatinized!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Loggins and Messina are both my servants, but they'll be {\i1}your{\i0} drill instructors. {from kono futari until loggins desu}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even I can't gelatinize water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to learn how?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to perform this technique as I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,20,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.44,Default,,0,0,20,,I'm obligated to learn your techniques!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.72,Default,,0,0,20,,Obligated?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,20,,Then you're also obligated to have a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.78,Default,,0,0,20,,Why don't you two boys introduce yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be especially helpful to know the names of the boy's we'll be {\i1}drilling{\i0} the next three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Respiration! {kokyuu da}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Temper your respiration, and your body, strength, and power will naturally follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to respire at least ten times within the span of a second! {from ichibyoukan ni until nare}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm dying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to inhale for ten minutes, and exhale for ten minutes, in that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to remove the respirator afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-What have I gotten myself into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:19.66,Toru Okawa,,0,0,0,,The rings will dissolve in seven days!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one final trial for you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our strength remains insufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a heart of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is batty! Bizarre, even!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.23,0:02:19.47,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Shijima no soko kara
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.27,0:02:26.63,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}mezameru sono hashiratachi toki wo koe
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.95,0:02:33.93,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Shinku no chishio ga
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.97,0:02:40.71,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}tachiagaru yuuki wo hikiawaseru
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.57,0:02:49.05,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Uketsugu ai wo sadame to yobu nara
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.51,0:02:55.41,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}hohoemu me de tsugi no te wo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.41,0:03:01.93,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Yami wo azamuite setsuna wo kawashite
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.59,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Yaiba surinuke yatsura no suki wo tsuke
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.01,0:03:11.61,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Tsuranuita omoi ga mirai wo hiraku
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.47,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}He's like a bloody stream!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.55,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Atsuku like a bloody stream
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.79,0:03:20.15,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ketsumyaku ni kizamareta innen ni
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.65,0:03:25.97,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ukiagaru kienai hokori no kizuna
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.49,0:03:31.79,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}nigirishimete
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.23,0:02:19.47,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}Once, four folks from the fires of Hell
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.27,0:02:26.63,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}awoke from their pillars after eons of eternal slumber.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.95,0:02:33.93,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}Their ambition for power assembled
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.97,0:02:40.71,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}the blood of a few bombastic braves.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.57,0:02:49.05,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}But one brave, whose fate was bound in his blood,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.51,0:02:55.41,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}shot a sly smirk at his destined demise.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.41,0:03:01.93,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}He would deceive the darkness and dodge the danger!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.59,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}He would exploit the flaws of the foes he faced!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.01,0:03:11.61,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}And his memory would live on for all posterity!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.47,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}He's like a bloody stream!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.55,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}He's blazing like a bloody stream
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.79,0:03:20.15,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}But would he be free of the cursed fate of his family?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.65,0:03:25.97,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}Who can say, but the bonds of these braves
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.49,0:03:31.79,Opening v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an2}will never be buried.
